# PIMES BLIND TEST REGISTRY

## Schema (Append-Only CSV)

```csv
Prediction_UUID,Input_UUID,Timestamp,Station,Prediction_Class,Confidence,Magnitude,Azimuth,Model_Version,SHA256,Evidence_UUID,Status
```

## Prediction Registry Example

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| Prediction_UUID | uuid | Unique prediction identifier |
| Input_UUID | uuid | Input waveform file hash |
| Timestamp | ISO 8601 UTC | Prediction generation time |
| Station | string | 3-letter BMKG station code |
| Prediction_Class | string | normal/unknown/precursor/earthquake/storm |
| Confidence | float [0,1] | Model confidence |
| Magnitude | float | Predicted magnitude (if applicable) |
| Azimuth | float | Predicted azimuth in degrees |
| Model_Version | string | e.g., "v2.0.0-rc2-freeze" |
| SHA256 | hex | Prediction file checksum |
| Evidence_UUID | uuid | Link to SEOS evidence record |
| Status | string | pending/reviewed/published |

## File Location

`d:\opt\pimes\pocc\BLIND_TEST_LEDGER\prediction_registry.csv`
